歌手被狗袭击后，迷幻色情松饼取消英国和欧洲巡演https://www.nme.com/news/music/psychedelic-porn-crumpets-cancel-uk-and-european-tour-after-singer-attacked-by-dog-3594326?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=psychedelic-歌手被狗袭击后色情松饼取消英国和欧洲巡演Tom SkinnerWed, 28 Feb 2024 15:09:19 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3594326 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/PsychedelicPornCrumpets-cancel-2024-UK-European-tour-dog-bite-face-news.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杰克·麦克尤恩 (Jack McEwan) 与迷幻色情松饼一起在舞台上现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/PsychedelicPornCrumpets-cancel-2024-UK-European-tour-dog-bite-face-news.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/PsychedelicPornCrumpets-cancel-2024-UK-European-tour-dog-bite-face-news-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/PsychedelicPornCrumpets-cancel-2024-UK-European-tour-dog-bite-face-news-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/PsychedelicPornCrumpets-cancel-2024-UK-European-tour-dog-bite-face-news-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/PsychedelicPornCrumpets-cancel-2024-UK-European-tour-dog-bite-face-news-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/PsychedelicPornCrumpets-cancel-2024-UK-European-tour-dog-bite-face-news-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我可能会用吸管吃烤晚餐一段时间”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/psychedelic-porn-crumpets-cancel-uk-and-european-tour-after-singer-attacked-by-dog-3594326">歌手被狗袭击后，《Psychedelic Porn Crumpets》取消了英国和欧洲巡演，并</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/PsychedelicPornCrumpets-cancel-2024-UK-European-tour-dog-bite-face-news.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杰克·麦克尤恩 (Jack McEwan) 与迷幻色情松饼一起在舞台上现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/PsychedelicPornCrumpets-cancel-2024-UK-European-tour-dog-bite-face-news.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/PsychedelicPornCrumpets-cancel-2024-UK-European-tour-dog-bite-face-news-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/PsychedelicPornCrumpets-cancel-2024-UK-European-tour-dog-bite-face-news-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/PsychedelicPornCrumpets-cancel-2024-UK-European-tour-dog-bite-face-news-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/PsychedelicPornCrumpets-cancel-2024-UK-European-tour-dog-bite-face-news-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/PsychedelicPornCrumpets-cancel-2024-UK-European-tour-dog-bite-face-news-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在主唱 Jack McEwan 被狗袭击后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/psychedelic-porn-crumpets">Psychedelic Porn Crumpets</a>被迫取消了 2024 年英国和欧洲巡演的剩余时间。</p><p>这支澳大利亚迷幻摇滚乐队上周在伯明翰（2 月 21 日）、格拉斯哥（22 日）和曼彻斯特（23 日）登台演出，进行了前三场演出。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/people-ceiling-psychedelic-porn-crumpets-raucous-uk-crowds-2497652">迷幻色情松饼在他们“喧闹”的英国节目中：“天花板上有人”</a></strong></li></ul><p>在三月份一系列欧洲头条新闻之前，本月已<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/Czsiiruyy45/?img_index=2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">计划</a>在利兹、布里斯托尔、伦敦和南安普顿举行更多演出。</p><p>然而，在 Crumpets 在利兹举行音乐会之前，麦克尤恩在 Instagram 上分享了一段视频，展示了他脸上被狗咬伤的痕迹。</p><p> “利兹！我们对此感到非常抱歉，但不幸的是，杰克今晚被狗咬伤，无法参加比赛。”乐队在这段在医院病房拍摄的视频中写道。</p><p> “缝了 100 针并注射了破伤风疫苗后，我们正在慢慢地将他重新组装起来。不幸的是，这意味着我们今晚无法参加利兹演出，但请保留好您的门票，我们正在尽快宣布重新安排的日期。”</p><p>后来，麦克尤恩在准备接受咬伤手术时与粉丝们分享了一些“相当坏的消息”。</p><p> “他们让我用上了这里的旧滴管。我基本上得把下巴刮掉，把老狗咬伤的所有感染都清除掉，”这位歌手在病床上解释道。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C3uwiXjNXLx/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" ba